==Dlighe de Charles==

Anns an [[Eòlas-nàdair]], tha '''Dlighe de Charles''' na '''dlighe ghais''' a tha na chuise sonraichte de [[Dlighe Ginearalta nan Gas]]. 

===A Reir Dlighe de Charles:=== 
Aig bruthachd cunbhalachd, airson màs cunbhalachd de gas foirfe, theid meudachadh neo lughadachadh 
air a thoirt, ann an co-riochd ri airdeachadh neo ioslachadh air a theasad teirmidinimeachd (tomhaiste le aonadan Ceilbhin).


B'e [[Ioseph Louis Gay-Lussac]] a fhoillich an Dlighe an 1802, ach thug e fianais do obair neo-fhoillsichte a rinn [[Jaques Charles]] mu deidhinn 1787. An luib an fhianais siud, chaidh ainmcheadh  air an dlighe airson Charles. Is co-cruthachd de Dlighe de Charles, [[Dlighe Úi Bhaoghail]] agus [[Dlighe Gay-Lussac]] a tha ann an [[Dlighe Aonaichte nan Gas]]. 

Gabhar dlighe ginearalta don ainm [[Dlighe nan Gas Foirfe]] le co-aontachadh de na tri dlighean ghais agus an [[Dlighe de Avagadro]].   
 
===Siolaicheas===

Is foirmle an dlighe:

'''V/T = k'''

far a bheil:

*V Toirt an aille
*T Teasad an aille, (tomhaiste an aonadan Ceilbhin)
*k na chunbhalach.

In other more thermodynamics-based definitions, the relationship between the fixed mass of a gas at constant pressure is inversely proportional to the temperature applied to the system, which can be further used by stipulating a system where α represents cubic expansivity of a gas, with θ representing the temperature measured of the system in Kelvins:

V \varpropto T

V = Vo(1 + αθ)

A ghleidh luach a' chunbhalaich k, re teasachadh de balgam aile gleidhte aig bruthachd cunbhalach, is fheudar don toirt a mheudaich. An co-riochd, aobhrachaidh fionnadh an aile lughadachadh anns an toirt. Chan fhiach do luach a' chunbhalaich a bhi dearbhta a chuir feum air an dlighe a dheanamh co-mheasadh air dà bhalgam de aile a tha fo bruthachd co-ionnan;
 
    \frac{V_1}{T_1} = \frac{V_2}{T_2} \qquad \mathrm{or} \qquad \frac {V_2}{V_1} = \frac{T_2}{T_1} \qquad \mathrm{or} \qquad V_1\cdot T_2 = V_2\cdot T_1.

Mar sin, mar a teid meudachadh an teasad, theid meudachadh an tomad.

A reir an teorig, nuair a ruigseas teasad an aille fior-neoni ruigsidh tomad an aille neoni cuideachd. Cha tachair sin anns an domhainn riochdail o chionns gun teid dluthachadh ri gach aile riochdail aig teas as airde na fior-neoni (0 K),

